  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SECURING 1000 REFUGEE CHILDREN RIGHT TO EDUCATION</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project will contribute to delivery of refugees education promise outlined in the Global Compact on Refugees. It will ensure return of refugee children to learning, reinforce the value of education and provide education benefits to those who are likely to be left furthest behind. The project will equip sixty (60) teachers in Kampala Capital City with the knowledge, skills and attitudes they need to ensure refugee children are able to learn and acquire the education of their life.</narrative>
  </description>
